				"\nCalculator (unless you can do trig in your head)" +
 
				"\n\nREMEMBER, if you need extra help throughout the game, you can ask for a hint \nby pressing �give me a hint�. " +
				"\n\nTHERE IS NO PENALTY FOR ASKING A HINT!");
